\lim_{x\to 1}\frac{\sqrt{x^2+3}-2}{x^2-1}=\lim_{t\to 0}\frac{\sqrt{t^2+2t+4}-2}{t^2+2t}=\lim_{t\to 0}2\frac{\sqrt{\frac{t^2+2t}{4}+1}-1}{t^2+2t}=\lim_{t\to 0}2\frac{t/4}{2t}=\frac{1}{4}
